body:
**Our issue:**

We have the following situation:
- A brand menu filter (HierarchicalMenu widget), which contains root brands and their sub-categories.
- It seems that HierarchicalMenu menu allows faceting by only one value - currently selected option.
- We have a use case where we need to add one or more additional values to the above one - in particular - to filter by the selected brand/sub-brand and in addition with `None` (adding OR filter).
- We tried to use `onSearchStateChange` to inject dynamically the additional facet filter, but seems that does not works for `HierarchicalMenu` since it only process the first element from `state.hierarchicalFacetsRefinements`.
- Also in case of fixing the above, consider changing the behaviour of the HierarchicalMenu widget as well - to support multi-values selection.

Our widget looks like this:
```
 <HierarchicalMenu
     key="brandMenu"
     attributes={['brand.lvl0', 'brand.lvl1']}
     separator="/"
     defaultRefinement={defaultRefinement}
     showParentLevel
  />
```                  
and 

```
class App extends Component {
   constructor(props) {

  ............

      this.searchParams = {
        hitsPerPage: 60,
        disjunctiveFacetsRefinements,
        filters,
        facetFilters
      };
    }

.............

  handleSearchStateChange(nextSearchState) {
    if (!this.mounted) {
      return;
    }
    onSearchStateChange(nextSearchState);

    const dynamicBrandFilters = ['brand.lvl0:None'];

    this.searchParams.facetFilters = {
      ...this.searchParams.facetFilters,
      ...dynamicBrandFilters,
    };
    
    this.setState({ searchState: nextSearchState });
  }
}
```

and
```
 <InstantSearch
   searchClient={this.algoliaClient}
   indexName={this.props.indexes.products}
   searchState={this.state.searchState}
   onSearchStateChange={this.handleSearchStateChange}
   resultsState={this.resultState}
 >
<Configure {...this.searchParams} />
```

**Expected behaviour:**
- We can dynamically add one or more additional (`OR`) facet filters to the  `HierarchicalMenu` current refinement, using `onSearchStateChange`.

Looking forward for any feedback or suggestion to workaround this (if possible).

Thank you in advance!
